@startuml Online Request Flow

title Pattern 1: Online Request (Happy Path)

participant Component
participant Hook
participant "React Query" as RQ
participant "API Client" as API
participant Backend
participant "Cache Manager" as Cache
participant IndexedDB

Component -> Hook: Request data
Hook -> RQ: Query
RQ -> API: Fetch
API -> Backend: HTTP Request
Backend --> API: Response
API -> Cache: Store in cache
Cache -> IndexedDB: putItem()
IndexedDB --> Cache: ✓
Cache --> API: ✓
API --> RQ: Data
RQ --> Hook: Data
Hook --> Component: Render

@enduml
